<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/logo.ico" type="image/x-icon" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
    <title>Recuperar Contraseña</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <section
      class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"
    >
      <div
        class="flex flex-col w-full max-w-md p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 pb-4">
          <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Logo" class="w-12 h-12" />
          <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-sky-900">
            Inmersión Musical
          </h1>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm font-light text-gray-500 pb-8">
          Ingresa tu correo electrónico para recibir el enlace de
          restablecimiento
        </p>

        <% if (typeof mensaje !== "undefined" && mensaje) { %>
        <div class="mb-4 p-3 rounded bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-center">
          <%= mensaje %>
        </div>
        <a
          href="/"
          class="w-full text-center text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-indigo-300 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm px-5 py-3 transition duration-150 ease-in-out mt-4"
        >
          Ir al inicio
        </a>
        <% } else { %>
        <form method="POST" action="/restablecer/enviar-reset" class="flex flex-col gap-6">
          <div>
            <label
              for="email"
              class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 text-sky-900"
              >Correo Electrónico</label
            >
            <div class="relative">
              <span
                class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 flex items-center pl-3 text-gray-400 pr-5"
              >
                <i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>
              </span>
              <input
                type="email"
                name="username"
                id="username"
                required
                placeholder="ejemplo@correo.com"
                class="p-2 pl-10 w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"
              />
            </div>
          </div>

          <button
            type="submit"
            class="w-full text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-indigo-300 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm px-5 py-3 transition duration-150 ease-in-out"
          >
            Reestablecer Contraseña
          </button>
        </form>
        <% } %>

        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-5 text-center">
          Donde las notas se convierten en sueños y cada alumno encuentra su
          propia melodía..
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>
